# LangSmith tracing is OPTIONAL. Leave LANGSMITH_API_KEY unset and tracing
# is skipped entirely (the @traceable decorators become no-ops).
# To enable: sign up at https://smith.langchain.com, create an API key,
# and uncomment the lines below.
# LANGSMITH_ENDPOINT=https://api.smith.langchain.com
# LANGSMITH_API_KEY=your_langsmith_key
# LANGSMITH_PROJECT=your_project_name

# defaults to groq, for testing i recommend openai/gpt-oss-120b since it works giga well
# for deepeval with groq, both must be set, since judge uses openai (for now at least, you can change)
# uncomment lines below to use one or both
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your_open_ai_key
# GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_key
